<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Your Story Has Been Approved - Warrior Sol</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #333;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #e88a49;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .section h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: #e88a49;
      }

      .section p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        color: #fff !important;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #e88a49;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .cta-button:hover {
        background-color: #d67a39;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #fff5ee;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }

      .social-links a {
        color: #e88a49;
        margin: 0 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .social-links a:hover {
        color: #d67a39;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>Congratulations, <%= userName %>!</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="section">
        <h1>Your Story Has Been Approved</h1>
        <p>
          We're excited to let you know that your story,
          <strong>"<%= title %>"</strong>, has been reviewed and approved by our team.
        </p>
        <p>
          Thank you for sharing your journey with the Warrior Sol community. Your voice matters and will inspire others.
        </p>

        <% if (typeof message !== 'undefined' && message) { %>
        <p><%= message %></p>
        <% } %>

        <p>
          Stay tuned for more updates and keep shining your light!
        </p>

        <a
          class="cta-button"
          href="<%= frontendUrl %>/community"
          target="_blank"
        >
          Visit the Warrior Sol Community â†’
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Stay connected</p>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="https://instagram.com/warriorsol">Instagram</a> |
          <a href="https://twitter.com/warriorsol">Twitter</a> |
          <a href="https://facebook.com/warriorsol">Facebook</a>
        </div>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Warrior Sol. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
